data.text:
The lineup of artists for this release is out of this world, featuring Mark Snow, Soul Coughing, Foo Fighters, William S. Burroughs, R.E.M., Nick Cave & The Bad Seeds, Frank Black, Danzing, Screamin' Jay Hawkins, Elvis Costello, Brian Eno, plus tracks performed by Sheryl Crow, Filter, Meat Puppets, Rob Zombie & Alice Cooper, and P.M. Dawn, which are making their first appearance on a vinyl release.

Tracklist

Side A

Mark Snow - X-Files Theme (Main Title)

Soul Coughing - Unmarked Helicopters

Sheryl Crow - On The Outside

Foo Fighters - Down In The Park

William S. Burroughs & R.E.M. - Star Me Kitten

Side B

Nick Cave and The Bad Seeds - Red Right Hand

Filter - Thanks Bro

Frank Black - Man of Steel

Meat Puppets - Unexplained

Side C

Danzig - Deep

Screamin' Jay Hawkins - Frenzy

Elvis Costello with Brian Eno - My Dark Life

Rob Zombie and Alice Cooper - Hands of Death (Burn Baby Burn)

Side D

P.M. Dawn - If You Never Say Goodbye

P.M. Dawn - The X-Files Theme (P.M. Dawn Remix)
